          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2157.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> basil</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>grated cheese</strong> and <strong>flaked almonds</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong></p>\n<p>Add 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and whizz until a smooth paste has formed – this is your <strong>homemade cheddar pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
